title: When do rookie QBs start, buy or sell Browns as AFC playoff contender (Football 05/14)
description:
Ryan Wilson joins Will Brinson to break down the over/unders for the number of games started by all the first-round rookie quarterbacks. Then they play a game of buy or sell with the AFC North mentor-less quarterbacks, the Cowboys usage of Tavon Austin and the Browns having a chance to make the wild card.
